text: Hi team and <@U0111JYSE23>, I am working with the N95 decon group (<http://N95decon.org|N95decon.org>) that is creating evidence-based protocols for N95 mask reprocessing. We would like to have some of the fact sheets translated to amharic (and oromifa, tigrigna, etc if preferred). These will guide hospital leaders and reprocessing staff on the proper protocols for N95 mask reprocessing for reuse. If anyone has the time for this please DM me - thank you!!
